/***************
Footer
***************/
footer {
  background: #fff url('../images/seaweed.jpg') repeat-x 0 0;
  padding: 142px 0;
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.7; 
}
footer ul {
  float: left;
  margin: 0 100px 50px 0; 
}
footer .list-heading {
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #333;
  margin-bottom: 30px;
  font-size: 17px; 
  font-family: 'Maven Pro', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}
footer a {
  color: #333;
}
footer li, 
footer p {
  color: #4D4D4D; 
  line-height: 30px;
}
footer li {
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.legal-copy {
  text-align: right;
  font-size: 10px;
}
```

